As this title is basically out of print in the US, this is your best chance of getting a copy of the complete uncut trailblazing series from Here TV.  This is not US region coded, so you will need a region free dvd player to enjoy.  Dante's Cove is a gay/lesbian themed supernatural drama with witches and warlocks and beautiful people.  This series is trailblazing for its frank and honest portrayal of gay men and lesbians without any stereotypes.  Of not, Stephen Amell of Arrow fame stars in season one as Adam before he hit it big as a superhero.  The story is engrossing, the acting above par, the original soundtrack is amazing, and the on location setting is beautiful.  Buckle up and enjoy the scary sexy ride of your life!
Everything OK nothing to blame about.
